title: BBC Love and Drugs on the Street Girls Sleeping Rough Series 1 1
description: Love and Drugs on the Street: Girls Sleeping Rough Sociopolitical Documentary hosted by Lily Murray, published by BBC in 2017 - English narration http://docuwiki.net/images/e/e0/Love-and-Drugs-on-the-Street-Girls-Sleeping-Rough-Cover.jpg Information ------------------------------ Love and Drugs on the Street: Girls Sleeping Rough Eye-opening stories of the daily lives of women sleeping rough on Brighton's streets. 1) Survival Filmed in Brighton and Hove, which has seen the UK's biggest increase in homelessness over the past year, we meet Paige, who is 21 and sleeps in a graveyard; Tanya, who is 7 months pregnant and sleeps rough with her partner; and Jo-Jo, who is 21, smoking spice and sleeping in shop doorways.
